Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，卡萊多之星就要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候請保持室內的亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請不要離電視太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有對於自己的將來有什麼設想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？醫生？各人的夢想都不一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.79,0:00:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要做自己想做的事是非常困難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.40,0:00:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要有絕對不放棄的信心！心！心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面終於到了美亞專人主頁大公開的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過突然改變風格不有點奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係，老闆都同意了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏預定要放上大家的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是阿娜的特別寫真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候拍的這個照片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.00,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜搞笑的時候偷拍的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人的照片都有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我本來是這麼打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.79,0:03:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.79,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這裏每天都有人辭職的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1天同時有3人辭職的事也有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才添加了照片人就走了，不是讓我很洩氣麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.00,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我最近加進了原創的小故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原創的故事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，可愛的故事，恐怖的故事，有很多哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑話有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空，有客人找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.29,0:04:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是日本人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的？誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前廳等你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.58,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.89,0:04:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊，我都等得不耐煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？我不能來這裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事，沒有，沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能來我很開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.27,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是站在這裏也不是回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是去喝茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在晚上的演出前回來就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.47,0:04:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去換衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是，這就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美怎麼會來這裏的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.27,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被選做了交換留學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在波士頓呆3個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的成績還是那麼好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要學習就可以了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習還是你行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.39,0:05:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊，人家都在學習的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.47,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你總是一個人跑出耍雜技，成績怎麼可能好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.20,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵，這個給你說了好多回了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我今天還真是吃了一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.60,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你還做了主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.29,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前總是說些“要成為卡萊多的明星”之類的傻話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還真讓你實現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.10,0:05:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能算是明星啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.29,0:05:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次只是得到特別允許\N和蕾拉小姐共同演出而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不……後悔嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有後悔過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還是那樣的留在日本，可能我會後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我只是覺得你好像在猶豫著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的你總是非常的自信……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說你不覺得很失禮嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把別人當作是迷茫中的傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我可沒有那個想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我們也該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.40,0:06:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上演出期間我就在後臺等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，因為我今晚要住在你那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒訂旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是我們的後臺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.10,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我在一起是沒有幸福生活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是靈魂也好，是什麼都沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，是空啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的朋友，真奈美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們在表演美亞主頁上面登錄的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空也來試試嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空來演這個角色吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎樣少女--一個逗哏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼玩意兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適合適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臺詞也太讓人難為情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是女孩子都能夠接受啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體狀況是不是不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強的話，會累垮身體的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也發現了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體不可能象蕾拉小姐那麼好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要每天和蕾拉小姐表演相同難度的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是必然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.19,0:08:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，我來幫你好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.39,0:08:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要莎拉小姐同意，老闆大致也會同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就利用練習室的設備\N以及飯後的時間來訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣，也就是說業餘訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不給你添麻煩就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能是添麻煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.29,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來，身上的疼痛是身體強度\N跟不上演技的難度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了嗎？他也不幹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個謠言原來是真的的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道大家真的都會退團嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團這回可真危險的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問，你們剛才說的那個事……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.19,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是大家因為你做主角而都辭職的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是，換了我就沒問題了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來的時候她就不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.19,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，因為我做了主角\N大家都不幹了的傳聞是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.60,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊，會相信那種謠言一點都不象你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是還有謠言說有人要建立新的劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡萊多劇團的競爭對手幹的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個退團？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊有空，蕾拉小姐還有由利，有什麼好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，原來還有不少的麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.39,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，真奈美，你在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.79,0:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能走走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.00,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.89,0:10:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上，下，上，下，上，下，上，下……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣，慢慢的來就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.79,0:10:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，我要加油……鍛煉身體才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.69,0:10:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼鍛煉身體，是趁機交男朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.19,0:10:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？健根本不是我的男朋友，根本不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……做了健身果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在一個小時之內喝的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對肌肉的恢復有好處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.89,0:10:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.20,0:10:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像是在哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，今天的事好像很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美，你要洗澡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……你在幹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，防患未然而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空，你有段時間沒理髮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你剪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.70,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼看來，好像是在美容院裏\N讓人理髮，我像是客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.60,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人理髮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空已經是卡萊多劇團的人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一直在注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想你表面上一副很強的無所畏懼的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是背地裏會不會暗暗哭泣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在擔心我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.40,0:12:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，我其實……是來看你後悔的樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.50,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……嗯，一切都很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再看一次你的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘傍晚的班機去波士頓，真奈美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE TWO ONE TWO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.20,0:13:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穩一點，輕一點，象羽毛一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的那個女孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說傍晚就要去波士頓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的……朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，空，你好象有點怕她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為……她總讓人有種難以抗拒的感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習的時候還在聊天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.80,0:13:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是以為自己是主角\N就可以得到原諒，就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師，我想邀請空共進午餐，可以原諒她嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.10,0:13:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以，由利說什麼都沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了，老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和由利共進午餐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.30,0:14:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自從我入團以來你一直在幫助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.10,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心啊，那麼你會跟著我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.10,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我希望你能到我這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在卡萊多劇團做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才……你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就會一舉退團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你能和我一起創建一個新的劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.10,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.70,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏沒有蕾拉，你就是頂級巨星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在……開玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在和我開玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.00,0:15:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團不是你想像中的那麼好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.70,0:15:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯欺騙了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你立刻回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為了你著想最好儘快給我答復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.90,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法了，一下子就有25個人同時退團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有停演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.20,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不過留下的那些孩子們太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連由利都……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空，糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始就不能再演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.30,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再演出了？騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.20,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天演出結束後有25個人要退團了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.20,0:15:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利走了，還帶走了其他骨幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.20,0:15:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.00,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就會一舉退團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你能和我一起創建一個新的劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利他真的這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了，我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就要結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解散了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.69,0:17:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，反正只要客人們高興就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.00,0:17:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是由利勸你退團了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接受了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.19,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.50,0:17:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸好象是說過想要收購卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.80,0:17:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拉斯維加斯的生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.09,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是發現的時候已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.09,0:17:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利似乎一直在盤算著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.80,0:17:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我似乎已經\N再也進不到由利的內心深處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.09,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船是不是再也用不到了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.69,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，少了20多個人，這個故事是沒法演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你長久以來的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你滿足了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.69,0:18:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，即使只看到了你現在的這個表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.59,0:18:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到……你失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.59,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，讓你看到奇怪的表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.19,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，我是來道歉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.30,0:19:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我說了奇怪的話了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我是來看你後悔的樣子"什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我說了那樣的話，你才……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.09,0:19:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是的，我的失敗不是因為那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是卡萊多劇團的危險關頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始就要停演一段時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.69,0:19:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才能夠和蕾拉小姐同台演出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團要解散了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.90,0:19:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卡萊多劇團要解散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不後悔來到這裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，決不後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.59,0:19:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個是我的夢想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我以前也一直說你是笨蛋笨蛋什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真的是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是很羡慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想是成為美容師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我的成績一直都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以父母對我的期望也很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.09,0:20:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來留學也是為了逃避這種兩難的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.80,0:20:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容師？很好啊，我支援你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說你是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.30,0:20:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說哪有那麼簡單的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.40,0:20:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能象你一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.09,0:20:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才來看看你後悔的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓我自己安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就根本提不起這種勇氣來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再幫我理髮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.69,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是真奈美的第一號客人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論真奈美以後選擇什麼樣的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會支援她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.00,0:21:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要為卡萊多劇團做點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要是解散了也是沒有辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.90,0:21:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我要盡全力不讓它解散，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.59,0:21:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也考慮了不少事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才象我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.00,0:21:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，還有，以後睡覺別老是睡的四仰八叉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.90,0:21:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美亞的劇本行嗎？老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.09,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行吧，太亂來了，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.70,0:21:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，老闆，我覺得使用這個劇本的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要少數的人就可以演出一場有趣的劇目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.80,0:22:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.90,0:22:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周之內必須讓這個劇本能夠上演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.50,0:22:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.10,0:22:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告：卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.70,0:22:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能已經超過莎士比亞了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.60,0:22:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們即將上演的是美亞自己編寫的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利的退團遊說還在繼續著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.10,0:22:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能盡力而為了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.70,0:22:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐雖然很反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.50,0:22:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過美亞一定會加油！加油！加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.70,0:22:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
